              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Irradiation time for each target was 30 min.",
                "Activation reaction 16O(t,n)18F (T1/2=109 min) was",
                "used for measurement of triton production cross",
                "section. 18F-collecting converters were composed of",
